  <p dir="ltr" style={{lineHeight: '1.38', marginTop: '0pt', marginBottom: '0pt'}}><span style={{fontSize: '11pt', fontFamily: 'Poppins,sans-serif', color: '#000000', backgroundColor: 'transparent', fontWeight: 400, fontStyle: 'normal', fontVariant: 'normal', textDecoration: 'none', verticalAlign: 'baseline', whiteSpace: 'pre-wrap'}}>We do not address anyone under the age of 13 and thus do not enforce COPPA. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal data, please contact us. If we become aware that we have collected personal data from anyone under the age of 13 without verification of parental consent, we take steps to remove that information from our servers.&nbsp;</span></p>
